<paragraph id="8BC9A055FFA7DC17FF4FFC28FCD94013" blockId="9.[151,1437,834,1041]" pageId="9" pageNumber="467">
Note. The forewing pattern, male and female genitalia characters, and dendrophages larvae (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE7DDA4FFA7DC17FB1DFC28FA2747CB" author="Walsingham, T. de &amp; Grey" box="[1221,1437,943,969]" pageId="9" pageNumber="467" pagination="911 - 1034" refId="ref8471" refString="Walsingham, T. de Grey (1908) Microlepidoptera of Tenerife. The Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London of the Year 1907, 911 - 1034, pls. LI - LIII. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1469 - 7998.1907. tb 06964. x" type="journal article" year="1908">Walsingham 1908:</bibRefCitation>
